Package edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.manager

Class AppList

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.app_manager.model.manager.AppList
public class AppList extends Object
Maintains a ArrayList of Applications with functionality to add and remove an Application from the list, search for an Application, update an Application, and return sublists.
Author:
Christine Weld
